  /// generated resources such as Model and Endpoint. Label keys and values can be no
  /// longer than 64 characters (Unicode codepoints), can only contain lowercase
  /// letters, numeric characters, underscores and dashes. International characters
  /// are allowed. See https://goo.gl/xmQnxf for more information and examples of
  /// labels.
  public let labels: [String: String]?

  /// Weight for KL Divergence regularization, Preference Optimization tuning only.
  public let beta: Float?

  /// The base teacher model that is being distilled. Distillation only.
  public let baseTeacherModel: String?

  /// The resource name of the Tuned teacher model. Distillation only.
  public let tunedTeacherModelSource: String?

  /// Multiplier for adjusting the weight of the SFT loss. Distillation only.
  public let sftLossWeightMultiplier: Float?

